        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
        <h1 class="display-5 mb-4">Experience Cinema, Reimagined</h1>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Discover a new era of movie-going with <strong>TicketZen</strong>. Our user-friendly
          platform offers seamless online booking, allowing you to
