          Enjoy exclusive perks like early bird discounts, loyalty rewards,
          and personalized recommendations. With just a few clicks, you can
          secure your tickets and embark on an unforgettable cinematic
          journey.
        </p>
        <p>
          <i class="fa fa-check text-divider me-3"></i>Easy and Intuitive
          Booking
        </p>
        <p>
          <i class="fa fa-check text-divider me-3"></i>Wide Range of Movies
        </p>
        <p>
          <i class="fa fa-check text-divider me-3"></i>Real-time Seat
          Selection
